{"tid":148061,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]除左北京電視機，近年來最黑哨係咪琴晚場阿記對拜仁？🤔","createTime":"2017-03-08T10:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:30:13.000Z","uid":5549,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58e3254b70fbd9f8a52af6e7ba59aa267ddb0847","tid":148061,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"1. 禾仔球12碼冇吹<br />\n2. 利雲果球12m係正常攞位，冇踢腳冇拉人，唔應該12m，更加唔應該有黃牌<br />\n3. 哥斯尼冇啦啦拎多張黃牌比人趕出場，睇佢都係正常反應，點都唔應該再拎黃牌<br />\n4. 全場都阿記球員既判罰都特別嚴，e.g.張伯倫有球冇心犯規都攞黃牌。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多，有睇場波就知，一面倒係拜仁得益，唔係誤判咁簡單。"},{"pid":"8adc97ef1ac033c21b83537b5b42fd8e1963ca33","tid":148061,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"ching近年來係幾多年"},{"pid":"09cec9151099ed2488f5b096b7ddccc7981fd5b9","tid":148061,"uid":872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"講到好似首回合阿狗冇黑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d564f97e1099e2dd44266438076bdf679225e92","tid":148061,"uid":533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"如果垃圾阿狗無黑哨，而家我諗佢地連第五都無撚埋"},{"pid":"8cde539a7c4e010b0426aef749fc57da060899e1","tid":148061,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到好似首回合阿狗冇黑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊次回合呀死熱狗！"},{"pid":"f92a867190880fc2d0529ece829d04cdc53cc70a","tid":148061,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講到好似首回合阿狗冇黑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊次回合呀死獌狗！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"960e91b4ae7ee69785db99ec9db108694e1711e7","tid":148061,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ching近年來係幾多年</blockquote><br />\n近十年"},{"pid":"66f9